                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>copy of the Pentateuch @ $25 the<lb/> price you name. I will try to dispose<lb/> of\n                the other books now that I know<lb/> their value.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I have sent (<date>Sunday</date>)<lb/> a list of the Lodges that\n                up<lb/> to that time had reported<lb/> (I had not yours of the <date>13th</date>\n                then)<lb/> to <placeName>N. Y.</placeName> for publication. You<lb/> will see them\n                mentioned in<lb/> the “Messenger” and if it<lb/> so please you add to the<lb/> list\n                those you have given<lb/> me (except Har Nevoh) which<lb/> I noticed in the <hi\n                    rend=\"underline\">Occident</hi> as<lb/> having acted and publish<lb/> in the best\n                of Jewish Periodicals<lb/> your own paper. I will<lb/> be gratified, or if you prefer<lb/>\n                <hi rend=\"underline\">wait</hi> till all returns are<lb/> in and then let me<lb/>\n                have 2 or 3 pages to<lb/> write up &amp; I will</p>\n            <p>In haste</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">With Sincerest wishes</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">for your health &amp; happiness</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">your Friend &amp; Bro</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(4)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">B. F. Peixotto</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p><addressee>Rev I. Leeser</addressee>. <placeName>Phila.</placeName></p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3mw2914d/canvas/p4"
